class Object_ImageMapHotspot extends gs.Object_Picture
    @objectCodecBlackList = ["parent"]
    
    @fromDataBundle: (data, context) ->
        return data
        
    @toDataBundle: (object, context) ->
        return { 
            enabled: object.enabled
            selected: object.selected
        }
   
    ###*
    * A game object used for pictures in a scene.
    *
    * @module gs
    * @class Object_Picture
    * @extends gs.Object_Visual
    * @memberof gs
    * @constructor
    ###
    constructor: () ->
        super()
        
gs.Object_ImageMapHotspot = Object_ImageMapHotspot
